== NBA生涯 ==
=== 遊走發展聯盟 ===
==== 2013-2014賽季 ====
居里落選[[2013年NBA选秀|2013年NBA選秀]]後，在2013年8月23日，獲[[金州勇士|金州勇士]]簽下非保證合約<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nba.com/2013/news/08/23/warriors-sign-seth-curry.ap/ |language=en |title=Warriors sign Seth Curry, reuniting brothers |publisher=NBA.com |date=2013-08-23 |accessdate=2015-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151031191609/http://www.nba.com/2013/news/08/23/warriors-sign-seth-curry.ap/ |archive-date=2015-10-31 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>；唯在出賽6場季前賽共7.2分鐘後，就被勇士隊釋出<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nba.com/warriors/news/warriors-waive-joe-alexander-seth-curry-and-dewayne-dedmon |language=en |title=Warriors Waive Joe Alexander, Seth Curry and Dewayne Dedmon |publisher=NBA.com |date=2013-10-25 |accessdate=2015-12-09 |archive-date=2016-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160812123204/http://www.nba.com/warriors/news/warriors-waive-joe-alexander-seth-curry-and-dewayne-dedmon |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

同年11月1日，居里被下放至[[NBA_G聯盟|NBA發展聯盟]]球隊[[聖克魯斯勇士|聖克魯斯勇士]]（Santa Cruz Warriors）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nba.com/dleague/santacruz/warriors_training_camp_roster_1314.html |language=en |title=Santa Cruz Warriors Announce Training Camp Roster |publisher=NBA.com |date=2013-11-06 |accessdate=2015-12-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150408235135/http://www.nba.com/dleague/santacruz/warriors_training_camp_roster_1314.html |archivedate=2015-04-08 }}</ref>，並在同月22日初次出戰發展聯盟，攻入36分<ref name="nba131224">{{cite web |url=http://www.nba.com/grizzlies/news/grizzlies-sign-seth-curry-131224 |language=en |title=Grizzlies sign Seth Curry |publisher=NBA.com |date=2013-12-24 |accessdate=2015-12-09 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309182427/http://www.nba.com/grizzlies/news/grizzlies-sign-seth-curry-131224 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同年12月24日，[[孟菲斯灰熊|孟菲斯灰熊]]簽下居里<ref name="nba131224" />。2014年1月5日，居里初次出戰NBA，為灰熊應戰[[底特律活塞|底特律活塞]]，下場比賽4分鐘；但同日被灰熊釋出<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nba.com/grizzlies/news/grizzlies-waive-seth-curry-140105 |language=en |title=Grizzlies waive Seth Curry |publisher=NBA.com |date=2014-01-05 |accessdate=2015-12-09 |archive-date=2015-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150424181503/http://www.nba.com/grizzlies/news/grizzlies-waive-seth-curry-140105 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。四日後，他回到聖塔克魯茲勇士。同年2月3日，入選NBA發展聯盟未來全明星陣容<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nba.com/dleague/news/nba_dleague_all_star_2014_02_03.html |language=en |title=Eighth Annual NBA D-League All-Star Game Features 16 Players With NBA Experience |publisher=NBA.com |date=2014-02-03 |accessdate=2015-12-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140207181043/http://www.nba.com/dleague/news/nba_dleague_all_star_2014_02_03.html |archivedate=2014-02-07 }}</ref>。

2014年3月21日，[[克里夫蘭騎士|克里夫蘭騎士]]跟居里簽下十天合約<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nba.com/cavaliers/releases/sign-curry-10-day-140321 |language=en |title=Cavs Sign Seth Curry to 10-Day Contract |publisher=NBA.com |date= |accessdate=2015-12-09 |archive-date=2016-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160621003033/http://www.nba.com/cavaliers/releases/sign-curry-10-day-140321 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。下一天，居里在他的第二場NBA賽事中對上[[侯斯頓火箭|侯斯頓火箭]]，在9分鐘內射入1個三分球<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nba.com/games/20140322/HOUCLE/gameinfo.html |language=en |title=Notebook: Rockets 118, Cavaliers 111 |publisher=NBA.com |date=2014-03-23 |accessdate=2015-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160330124057/http://www.nba.com/games/20140322/HOUCLE/gameinfo.html |archive-date=2016-03-30 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。其後騎士隊決定不續約<ref>{{cite web |url=http://basketball.realgm.com/wiretap/232689/Cavaliers-Decide-Not-To-Sign-Seth-Curry-To-Second-10-Day-Contract |language=en |title=Cavaliers Decide Not To Sign Seth Curry To Second 10-Day Contract |publisher=RealGM |date=2015-03-30 |accessdate=2015-12-09 |archive-date=2015-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222102639/http://basketball.realgm.com/wiretap/232689/Cavaliers-Decide-Not-To-Sign-Seth-Curry-To-Second-10-Day-Contract |dead-url=no }}</ref>，居里亦回去聖塔克魯茲勇士繼續發展聯盟的賽季。在2013-2014賽季，他為聖塔克魯茲勇士打了38場賽事，場均得分19.7分，3.1個籃板球，5.8次助攻，1.4次搶截<ref name="D-League">{{cite web |url=http://www.basketball-reference.com/dleague/players/c/curryse01d.html |language=en |title=Seth Curry D-League Stats |publisher=Basketball-Reference.com |date= |accessdate=2015-12-09 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924050042/http://www.basketball-reference.com/dleague/players/c/curryse01d.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在效力聖塔克魯茲勇士期間，居里跟隊友麥可·湯普森（Mychel Thompson）同為後衛。與此同時，他們各自的兄弟——[[史蒂芬·居里|史蒂芬·居里]]和[[克雷·湯普森|克雷·湯普森]]——亦一同效力金州勇士，這對後場組合合稱「[[浪花兄弟|浪花兄弟]]」<ref>{{cite web |author=Anthony Oliva |url=http://www.nba.com/dleague/news/meet_the_sc_splash_brothers_2014_04_23.html |language=en |title=Meet the SC Splash Brothers |publisher=NBA.com |date=2014-04-23 |accessdate=2015-12-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160610060312/http://www.nba.com/dleague/news/meet_the_sc_splash_brothers_2014_04_23.html |archivedate=2016-06-10 }}</ref>。

==== 2014-2015賽季 ====
2014年7月，居里加入[[奧蘭多魔術隊|奧蘭多魔術]]以參與[[2014年NBA夏季聯賽|奧蘭多夏季聯賽]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nba.com/magic/orlando-magic-announce-roster-southwest-airlines-orlando-pro-summer-league |language=en |title=Orlando Magic Announce Roster for Southwest Airlines Orlando Pro Summer League |publisher=NBA.com |date=2014-07-07 |accessdate=2015-12-09 |archive-date=2014-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141021215504/http://www.nba.com/magic/orlando-magic-announce-roster-southwest-airlines-orlando-pro-summer-league |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其後加入[[鳳凰城太陽|鳳凰城太陽]]並參與洛杉磯夏季聯賽<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nba.com/suns/news/suns-2014-summer-league-roster-announced |language=en |title=Suns' 2014 Summer League Roster Announced |publisher=NBA.com |date=2014-07-07 |accessdate=2015-12-09 |archive-date=2015-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151101085009/http://www.nba.com/suns/news/suns-2014-summer-league-roster-announced |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他在同年9月24日跟魔術隊簽約<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.foxsports.com/florida/story/seth-curry-signed-orlando-magic-free-agents-092914 |language=en |title=Seth Curry among four free agents signed by Magic |publisher=FOXSports.com |date=2014-09-24 |accessdate=2015-12-09 |archive-date=2016-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160512211728/http://www.foxsports.com/florida/story/seth-curry-signed-orlando-magic-free-agents-092914 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。直屬奧蘭多魔術的[[艾利灣海鷹|艾利灣海鷹]]以NBA發展聯盟選秀第一輪選籤，換取居里在發展聯盟的比賽權<ref>{{cite web |url=http://erie.dleague.nba.com/news/bayhawks-acquire-returning-player-rights-of-seth-curry/ |language=en |title=BayHawks Acquire Returning Player Rights of Seth Curry |publisher=NBA.com |date=2014-12-30 |accessdate=2015-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304131225/http://erie.dleague.nba.com/news/bayhawks-acquire-returning-player-rights-of-seth-curry/ |archive-date=2016-03-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。在訓練營後，魔術隊在10月25日決定釋出居里<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.orlandopinstripedpost.com/2014/10/25/7070417/orlando-magic-training-camp-2014-roster-cuts-peyton-siva-seth-curry |language=en |title=Orlando Magic training camp: Team waives Seth Curry, Peyton Siva, and two others |publisher=Orlando Pinstriped Post |date=2014-10-25 |accessdate=2015-12-09 |archive-date=2015-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151224001831/http://www.orlandopinstripedpost.com/2014/10/25/7070417/orlando-magic-training-camp-2014-roster-cuts-peyton-siva-seth-curry |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他其後加入艾利灣海鷹並參加訓練營<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nba.com/dleague/erie/bayhawks_acquire_four_players_2014_10_30.html |language=en |title=BayHawks Acquire Four Players, Complete Coaching Staff |publisher=NBA.com |date=2014-10-30 |accessdate=2015-12-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160610055533/http://www.nba.com/dleague/erie/bayhawks_acquire_four_players_2014_10_30.html |archivedate=2016-06-10 }}</ref>。11月14日，他首次為海鷹隊出戰，對上[[爱达荷奔腾|愛達荷奔騰]]並勝出，投24中9得23分<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nba.com/dleague/games/20141114/ERIIDA/gameinfo.html |language=en |title=BayHawks at Stampede Game Info – November 14, 2014 |publisher=NBA.com |date=2014-11-14 |accessdate=2015-12-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160610055800/http://www.nba.com/dleague/games/20141114/ERIIDA/gameinfo.html |archivedate=2016年6月10日 }}</ref>。2015年2月4日，居里再次入選NBA發展聯盟未來全明星陣容<ref>{{cite web |url=http://dleague.nba.com/news/nba-development-league-all-star-game-rosters-2015/ |language=en |title=Thirteen NBA Veterans Headline Rosters for NBA Development League All-Star Game Presented by Kumho Tire |publisher=NBA.com |date=2015-02-04 |accessdate=2015-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150205023335/http://dleague.nba.com/news/nba-development-league-all-star-game-rosters-2015/ |archive-date=2015-02-05 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2015年3月11日，[[鳳凰城太陽|鳳凰城太陽]]因控球後衞[[布兰登·奈特|布蘭登·奈特]]扭傷左腳腳踝，而跟居里簽下十天合約<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nba.com/suns/press-release/suns-sign-seth-curry-10-day-contract |language=en |title=Suns Sign Seth Curry to 10-Day Contract |publisher=NBA.com |date=2015-03-11 |accessdate=2015-12-09 |archive-date=2015-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151103152015/http://www.nba.com/suns/press-release/suns-sign-seth-curry-10-day-contract |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="nba150311">{{cite web |url=http://www.nba.com/games/20150311/MINPHX/gameinfo.html |language=en |title=Markieff Morris leads Suns past Timberwolves, 106-97 |publisher=NBA.com |date=2015-03-11 |accessdate=2015-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151030023143/http://www.nba.com/games/20150311/MINPHX/gameinfo.html |archive-date=2015-10-30 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。他在該日以太陽隊球員身份上陣，該場太場隊以106-97打敗[[明尼蘇達木狼|明尼蘇達木狼]]<ref name="nba150311" />。十日後（3月21日），太陽隊不續約。替太陽隊打了兩場比賽、平均每場上場3.9分鐘的居里回到艾利灣海鷹<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.oursportscentral.com/services/releases/?id=4940646 |language=en |title=Curry Rejoins BayHawks |publisher=OurSports Central |date=2015-03-21 |accessdate=2015-12-09 |archive-date=2015-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150927210513/http://www.oursportscentral.com/services/releases/?id=4940646 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2014-2015賽季，他為艾利灣海鷹打了43場賽事，場均得分23.8分，3.9個籃板球，4.2次助攻，1.4次搶截<ref name="D-League" />。
=== 薩克拉門托帝王隊 ===
==== 2015-2016賽季 ====
2015年7月，居里加入[[新奧爾良塘鵝|新奧爾良塘鵝]]並出戰[[NBA夏季聯賽|NBA夏季聯賽]]<ref>{{cite web |author=Jim Eichenhofer |url=http://www.nba.com/pelicans/news/new-orleans-pelicans-summer-roster-includes-four-players-official-nba-experience |language=en |title=New Orleans Pelicans summer roster includes four players with official NBA experience |publisher=NBA.com |date=2015-07-02 |accessdate=2015-12-09 |archive-date=2015-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151101164127/http://www.nba.com/pelicans/news/new-orleans-pelicans-summer-roster-includes-four-players-official-nba-experience |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他在夏季聯賽中每場平均投進24.3分，並獲得NBA發展聯盟年度第一隊的榮譽<ref>{{cite web |author=Ben Golliver |url=http://www.si.com/nba/2015/07/20/all-nba-summer-league-team-spurs-wolves-lakers-kyle-anderson-karl-anthony-towns |language=en |title=All-NBA Summer League team: Curry, Anderson lead diverse group |publisher=[[運動畫刊|運動畫刊]] |date=2015-07-20 |accessdate=2015-12-09 |archive-date=2016-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160112134731/http://www.si.com/nba/2015/07/20/all-nba-summer-league-team-spurs-wolves-lakers-kyle-anderson-karl-anthony-towns |dead-url=no }}</ref>。7月22日，他跟[[薩克拉門托帝王|薩克拉門托帝王]]簽下2年200萬美元，並附有第二年球員選項的合約，多年遊走在發展聯盟和NBA的居里終於獲得一紙保證約<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nba.com/kings/news/kings-sign-acy-curry-dukan |language=en |title=Kings Sign Quincy Acy, Seth Curry and Duje Dukan |publisher=NBA.com |date=2015-07-22 |accessdate=2015-12-09 |archive-date=2015-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151202104046/http://www.nba.com/kings/news/kings-sign-acy-curry-dukan |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=John Reid |url=http://www.nola.com/pelicans/index.ssf/2015/07/pelicans_lose_out_on_guard_set.html |language=en |title=Pelicans lose out on guard Seth Curry after Sacramento Kings extend 2-year guaranteed deal |publisher=NOLA.com |date=2015-07-21 |accessdate=2015-12-09 |archive-date=2015-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151026022246/http://www.nola.com/pelicans/index.ssf/2015/07/pelicans_lose_out_on_guard_set.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。10月30日，他首次以帝王隊球員身分上場比賽，投2中1得2分，1助攻1籃板；該場對[[洛杉磯湖人|洛杉磯湖人]]勝132-114<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nba.com/games/20151030/LALSAC/gameinfo.html |language=en |title=Rondo, Cousins lead Kings to 132-114 win over Lakers |publisher=NBA.com |date=2015-10-31 |accessdate=2015-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160123231011/http://www.nba.com/games/20151030/LALSAC/gameinfo.html |archive-date=2016-01-23 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。11月28日，帝王對[[金州勇士|金州勇士]]一戰進入垃圾時間後，居里於第四節上場，9分鐘內投進3個三分球，投4中3得9分
=== 達拉斯獨行俠隊 ===
==== 2016-2017賽季 ====
2016年7月，柯瑞以2年600萬美元加盟了[[達拉斯小牛|達拉斯小牛]]。2017年1月30日 柯瑞在對[[圣安东尼奥马刺|馬刺]]的比賽，創下了個人得分新紀錄24分。之後又在2017年2月25日對[[明尼蘇達灰狼|明尼蘇達灰狼]]的比賽中刷新了個人單場得分31分，三天後，在對[[邁阿密熱火|邁阿密熱火]]的比賽，獲得了生涯次高的29分。

